      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments conducted by a second qualified analyst; discrepancies resolved and documented.",
      "rationale": "A second FDA biomedical engineer independently reviewed all boundary condition definitions, contact pair assignments, and material property inputs against the simulation protocol. Three minor discrepancies identified and corrected prior to final runs. Use error risk assessed as low."
