      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa) and Poisson's ratio (0.34) taken from MMPDS-12 for Ti-6Al-4V ELI. Geometry inputs derived from CMM measurements of five representative screws and rods; dimensional variability propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000). Input uncertainty contribution to total uval quantified and included in E/uval metric."
