      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 test constructs from production lots; lot traceability documented; dimensional verification confirms conformance to design drawings.",
      "rationale": "Eleven constructs assembled from production-representative screws and rods from two separate lots. CMM dimensional verification confirmed all components within drawing tolerances. Lot traceability records archived. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison per ASME V&V 40 guidance."
