      "rationale": "CMM-measured dimensions used directly as FEA geometry inputs. Material certificates confirm elastic modulus within 2% of MMPDS-12 nominal. Boundary condition equivalency verified by comparing machine compliance contributions. All discrepancies between model and test inputs quantified and incorporated into uval."
