      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs; percent difference < 10% for each QoI.",
      "rationale": "Stiffness: E/uval = 0.82, percent difference = 3.1%. Yield force: E/uval = 1.14, percent difference = 4.7%. Force at 40 mm: E/uval = 1.31, percent difference = 6.2%. All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Model predictions are within validation uncertainty for all outputs of interest."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
