      "rationale": "Validation constructs are identical in design to the intended-use device. Loading protocol (ASTM F1717 compression-bending) is the same as the regulatory submission test. Two-laboratory cross-validation strengthens confidence in result reproducibility. The validation context is highly representative of the COU; no significant extrapolation is required."
